extends /layouts/main
block content
  .container-fluid
  .header-dimmer.gray-dark-bg
    .container
      .header
        .logo
          a(href="http://theironyard.com"): img(src="/images/iron-yard-logo.svg")
        .nav
          .primary-nav
            ul
              li 
                a(href="/locations") Locations
              li 
                a(href="/events") Events
              li
                a(href="/academy") Academy
              li 
                a(href="/accelerator") Accelerator
          
          .secondary-nav
            ul
              li 
                a(href="/jobs") Jobs
              li
                a(href="/about") About
              li
                a(href="http://news.theironyard.com") News
              li
                a(href="http://blog.theironyard.com") Blog

  .container(style="max-width:1000px")
    .three-col-cta.row
      .col-lg-2.col-sm-2
        .image-box
          img(src="images/home/home-page-icons-code-school.png")
      .col-lg-7.col-sm-6(style="padding-right:0")
        a(style="text-decoration:none; color:#39474e" href="/academy"): h3 Intensive Code School
        p(style="margin-top:0px"): em Become a professional programmer and get a great job.
        p The Iron Yard Academy teaches intensive, three-month courses that mentor you into a professional junior-level programmer. Our program goes far beyond tactical skills and teaches you to think like a software engineer. Programming is a lifelong study, and our process shows you to learn how to learn so you remain highly valuable for the rest of your career.
      .col-lg-3.col-sm-4.cta-box
        a(href="/academy").btn Learn More
    hr    
    .three-col-cta.row
      .col-lg-2.col-sm-2
        .image-box
          img(src="images/home/home-page-icons-accelerator.png")
      .col-lg-7.col-sm-6(style="padding-right:0")
        a(style="text-decoration:none; color:#39474e" href="/accelerator"): h3 Startup Accelerator
        p(style="margin-top:0px"): em We’re interested in building strong, sustainable businesses that add real value to customers’ lives.
        p Speaking the same language? We’d love for you to join us. Whether your goal is a Series A round, building a team and bootstrapping, or utilizing Kickstarter, we have a place for you. We run three programs a year, a digital health program and an open tech program and a green tech program.
      .col-lg-3.col-sm-4.cta-box
        a(href="/accelerator").btn Learn More
    hr    
    .three-col-cta.row
      .col-lg-2.col-sm-2
        .image-box  
          img(src="images/home/scratch-logo.png")
      .col-lg-7.col-sm-6(style="padding-right:0")
        a(style="text-decoration:none; color:#39474e" href="/academy#kids"): h3 Kids Education
        p(style="margin-top:0px"): em We believe in investing in the local tech economy for the long-run, and that means impacting the next generation.
        p Students in our intensive courses are required to volunteer, teach and run our Kids programs as a part of their involvement in the Academy. (Not only does this develop a giving mindset, but it helps them communicate things they’ve learned—an essential skill as they grow into management positions in their careers.)
      .col-lg-3.col-sm-4.cta-box
        a(href="/academy#kids").btn Learn More
    hr    
    .three-col-cta.row
      .col-lg-2.col-sm-2
        .image-box  
          img(src="images/home/home-page-icons-cowork.png")
      .col-lg-7.col-sm-6(style="padding-right:0")
        a(style="text-decoration:none; color:#39474e" href="/locations"): h3 Coworking Spaces
        p(style="margin-top:0px"): em We run cutting-edge coworking spaces across the nation.
        p Our Coworking spaces are comprised of designers, strategists, developers, writers and entrepreneurs. We’re not talking about fly-by-night freelancers. They’re independent business owners, connected with each other through the space they share and the projects they inevitably develop together.
      .col-lg-3.col-sm-4.cta-box
        a(href="/locations").btn Learn More
    hr    
    .three-col-cta.row
      .col-lg-2.col-sm-2
        .image-box  
          img(src="images/home/home-page-icons-grok.png")
      .col-lg-7.col-sm-6(style="padding-right:0")
        a(style="text-decoration:none; color:#39474e" href="/grok"): h3 GROK
        p(style="margin-top:0px"): em A conference with no heroes, just people hungry for tectonic shifts in thinking and doing.
        p Grok is an invitation. Come to one of the best small cities in the nation. Talk, listen, eat and drink with world class people asking a ton of hard questions, digging into great issues, and making headway on some decent real-world solutions.
      .col-lg-3.col-sm-4.cta-box
        a(href="/grok").btn Learn More

  .horizontal-section.gray-light-bg(style="margin-bottom:-40px")    
    .callout-box(style="margin-bottom:0")
      h2 Who We Are
      hr
      p(style="margin-bottom:0") The Iron Yard exists to create exceptional value for people and their ideas through code education, startup accelerators and coworking spaces. Through our broad, deep and growing network of teachers, programmers, designers, entrepreneurs, investors, employers and coworking spaces we have developed a thriving community where serendipity happens en-masse.
